{
  "info": {
    "name": "Gudang Planet — Ops Jabatans",
    "description": "Collection untuk endpoint Management Jabatan modul Operasional.\n\n**Base URL:** `{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/jabatans`\n\n**Auth:** Bearer token dari `POST /api/v1/login`.\n\n**Salary edit log:** Perubahan `daily_rate` otomatis tercatat di `GET /api/v1/operational/edit-logs` dengan `loggable_type: 'abs_jabatans'`.\n\n**Demo credentials (company 1):**\n| Role | Phone | Password |\n|------|-------|----------|\n| SUPERADMIN | 085155118899 | superadmin_gp |\n| ADMIN | 081122223333 | admin_gp |\n| HRD | 081155556666 | hrd_gp |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "uuid", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"081122223333\",\n  \"password\": \"admin_gp\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login sebagai ADMIN. Token otomatis disimpan ke collection variable `token`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (HRD)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"081155556666\",\n  \"password\": \"hrd_gp\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login sebagai HRD. Token otomatis disimpan ke collection variable `token`."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "List Jabatans",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "const json = pm.response.json();",
              "if (json.data && json.data.data && json.data.data.length > 0) {",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('uuid', json.data.data[0].uuid);",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/jabatans?per_page=15&order_by=name&order_by_value=ASC",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "jabatans"],
          "query": [
            { "key": "per_page", "value": "15", "description": "Jumlah per halaman" },
            { "key": "order_by", "value": "name", "description": "Kolom sorting (name, daily_rate, created_at)" },
            { "key": "order_by_value", "value": "ASC", "description": "ASC atau DESC" },
            { "key": "search", "value": null, "description": "Cari berdasarkan nama jabatan" }
          ],
          "variable": []
        },
        "description": "Mendapatkan daftar semua jabatan.\n\n**Role akses:** SUPERADMIN, OWNER, ADMIN, HRD"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Create Jabatan",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "const json = pm.response.json();",
              "if (json.data && json.data.uuid) {",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('uuid', json.data.uuid);",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Staff Gudang\",\n  \"daily_rate\": 75000\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/jabatans",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "jabatans"]
        },
        "description": "Membuat jabatan baru.\n\n**Role akses:** SUPERADMIN, ADMIN, HRD"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Show Jabatan",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/jabatans/{{uuid}}",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "jabatans", "{{uuid}}"]
        },
        "description": "Detail jabatan.\n\n**Role akses:** SUPERADMIN, OWNER, ADMIN, HRD"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Update Jabatan",
      "request": {
        "method": "PUT",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Staff Gudang Senior\",\n  \"daily_rate\": 85000,\n  \"reason\": \"Penyesuaian UMR 2026\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/jabatans/{{uuid}}",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "jabatans", "{{uuid}}"]
        },
        "description": "Update jabatan. Jika `daily_rate` berubah, otomatis tercatat ke edit logs.\n\n**Role akses:** SUPERADMIN, ADMIN, HRD\n\nField opsional:\n- `reason` — alasan edit (tercatat di edit log)"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Delete Jabatan",
      "request": {
        "method": "DELETE",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/jabatans/{{uuid}}",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "jabatans", "{{uuid}}"]
        },
        "description": "Hapus jabatan (soft delete). Gagal (422) jika masih digunakan oleh karyawan.\n\n**Role akses:** SUPERADMIN, ADMIN, HRD"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "List Edit Logs",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/operational/edit-logs?loggable_type=abs_jabatans&per_page=15",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "operational", "edit-logs"],
          "query": [
            { "key": "loggable_type", "value": "abs_jabatans", "description": "Filter: abs_jabatans, ops_incomes, ops_expenses" },
            { "key": "per_page", "value": "15", "description": "Jumlah per halaman" }
          ],
          "variable": []
        },
        "description": "Mendapatkan riwayat edit log. Filter `loggable_type=abs_jabatans` untuk melihat riwayat perubahan salary jabatan.\n\n**Role akses:** SUPERADMIN, OWNER, ADMIN, HRD"
      }
    }
  ]
}
